column4: Collection of data sources used in Statistical Post Processing.  In some cases post-processed output from one technique is used as a source for another technique.
Parameter category of physical atmospheric properties

In the MOS 2000 system, a coded representation of present weather information captured from an observation (e.g., METAR). This information is distilled into three integers (with inherent data loss). This collection interprets the coded values.  For an explanation, see TDL (MDL) Office Note 00-1, 13.21-22.
